{"tid":2147460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[健康碼推手]「建設力量」發表聯合聲明支持政府施政及經濟變革","createTime":"2020-08-09T09:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T11:30:33.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aecaa1f11e97bf0476afca757ae758d2ab738ea9","tid":2147460,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542705-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542705-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=334d7ece\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542705-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d4f799a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542705-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n由建制派發起的「建設力量」發表「香港要變革，攜手創明天」聯合聲明，支持政府施政及經濟變革。出席人員包括立法會建制派班長廖長江、民建聯主席李慧琼、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀、自由黨主席張宇人等。<br />\n<br />\n建設力量表示，中央派員協助擴大核酸檢測及建設方艙醫院，希望政府善用支援，盡快控制疫情，推動健康碼互認，逐步恢復兩地人員及經貿活動往來，又呼籲政府開展基建項目，增加臨時職位，完善失業援助制度，協助市民渡過經濟寒冬。<br />\n<br />\n被問到美國宣布制裁，葉劉淑儀形容美方橫蠻無理，認為推動國家安全是天經地義，制裁實質影響不大。葉劉淑儀形容，香港淪為兩國角力的棋子，未來或出現動盪，但香港金融中心的地位難以動搖，她認為政府仍然需要改革。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1542705_1_20200809163637.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1542705_1_20200809163637.jpg&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=74d457eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1542705_1_20200809163637.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7個人，無人敢用底褲罩，而且，犯咗599雞限聚令喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180bf3735a1c963ee0047ee0f54e3d004bca4a2d","tid":2147460,"uid":3860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:18:02.000Z","msg":"香港要變革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家個特首佢地揀，行會全部係賣港派，立法會又係賣港派話事<br />\n<br />\n要變革係咪變走自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f333affb97a039c0909ea9a8aef066baad69f72","tid":2147460,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"推啦，賣港賊"},{"pid":"883b756c0db01dd8d2d42f89bf3d09b212358b5c","tid":2147460,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"鬥地主鬥財主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f75d4168538932ddff5dc46e781d9130fc4fa7","tid":2147460,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"商家佬變CONDOM啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c45f87f535dde9518f6ac93dbd1c885f544e8e5","tid":2147460,"uid":281437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"消滅奶共狗"},{"pid":"9e414b89327687f54dccd4f77c65dea3d3445dfc","tid":2147460,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r